Notices under this section shall advise the recipient of the following:
The name, address, telephone number and name of the hospital's administrator;
The hospital's policies concerning visitation and other communications;
The right of the parent or other person exercising custodial control or supervision to participate in the child's treatment; and
The right of the parent or other person exercising custodial control or supervision to participate in any proceedings under this chapter, including the right to seek discharge of the child under KRS 645.230.
